thread.title: BRIEF-SB Financial Group Reports Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.64

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-SB Financial Group Reports Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.64
text:
Jan 25 (Reuters) - Sb Financial Group Inc:
* SB FINANCIAL GROUP, INC. ANNOUNCES FOURTH-QUARTER AND FULL-YEAR 2017 RESULTS
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.64 * IN Q4, ‍IMPACT OF DEFERRED TAX LIABILITY RECAPTURE WAS AN INCREASE IN NET INCOME OF $1.7 MILLION, OR $0.27 PER SHARE​
* ‍QTRLY NET INTEREST INCOME OF $7.7 MILLION, WAS UP 15.2 PERCENT FROM YEAR-AGO QUARTER, AND UP 5.4 PERCENT FROM LINKED QUARTER​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
